OL,3,CFormer Co-op Bank boss jailed for
OL,4,Cthree years over #100,000 fraud
OL,6,FFormer Co-operative Bank chairman Paul
OL,7,FFlowers ` who stole nearly #100,000
OL,8,Ffrom an elderly woman to spend on
OL,9,Fdrugs, holidays and gifts for himself
OL,10,F` has been jailed for three years.
OL,12,FFlowers, 74, a former Labour
OL,13,Fcouncillor and church minister, had
OL,14,Fbetrayed his friend of many years,
OL,15,FMargaret Jarvis, to plunder her cash,
OL,16,FManchester Crown Court heard.
