OL,3,CFormer Co-op Bank boss jailed for
OL,4,Cthree years over #100,000 fraud
OL,6,FThe defendant was brought into court
OL,7,Fusing a walking stick. He had handed
OL,8,Fhimself in to police after a judge had
OL,9,Fissued a warrant for his arrest when
OL,10,Fhe failed to appear for his sentencing
OL,11,Ftwo weeks ago.
OL,13,FJudge Nicholas Dean KC, Recorder of
OL,14,FManchester, said: "This is a story of
OL,15,Fbetrayal, no less than that. Betrayal
OL,16,Fby you of an old friend, someone who
OL,17,Ftrusted you, who had every reason to
OL,18,Fbelieve she could trust you.
